<Layout 
	title="About Stockton Fencing Co. | 15+ Years Experience | Licensed Contractors" 
	description="Meet Stockton's trusted fence experts with 15+ years experience. Licensed, bonded & insured contractors specializing in residential & commercial fencing throughout San Joaquin County." 
	canonicalUrl="/about">
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="hero-image-container">
			<picture class="hero-picture">
				<source srcset="/images/internal-page-fence-header.webp" type="image/webp">
				<img src="/images/internal-page-fence-header.webp" alt="Stockton Fencing Co team at work - professional fence installation" class="hero-image" loading="eager" width="1200" height="400" />
			</picture>
			<div class="hero-overlay">
				<div class="hero-content">
					<h1>About Our Network</h1>
					<p>Connecting you with trusted fencing professionals throughout Stockton</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="our-story">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="story-content">
				<div class="story-text">
					<h2>Our Mission</h2>
					<p>We connect homeowners and businesses throughout Stockton with experienced, professional fencing contractors who deliver quality workmanship and reliable service. Our network includes trusted professionals with years of experience serving the San Joaquin Valley.</p>
					
					<p>Every contractor in our network shares our commitment to honest work, fair pricing, and treating every customer with respect. We believe in building lasting relationships through quality service and transparent communication.</p>
					
					<p>Whether you need a new fence installation, repairs, or maintenance, we'll connect you with the right professional for your project. Our contractors have successfully completed thousands of projects throughout Stockton County, building trust one fence at a time.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="story-image">
					<div class="image-placeholder">
						<div class="placeholder-icon">📸</div>
						<h3>Professional Network</h3>
						<p>Trusted Contractors<br/>Throughout Stockton</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="values">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Our Core Values</h2>
			<div class="values-grid">
				<div class="value-item">
					<div class="value-icon">🔨</div>
					<h3>Quality Craftsmanship</h3>
					<p>Our contractors take pride in every fence they install. Using quality materials and proven techniques, they build fences that withstand Stockton's varied weather conditions and maintain their appearance over time.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="value-item">
					<div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
					<h3>Transparent Service</h3>
					<p>Our network contractors believe in fair pricing and transparent communication. They provide detailed written estimates and maintain honest business practices throughout your project.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="value-item">
					<div class="value-icon">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>
					<h3>Professional Care</h3>
					<p>Our contractors understand the importance of home and community. They treat your property with care and respect, maintaining the highest standards of professionalism.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="value-item">
					<div class="value-icon">🌱</div>
					<h3>Local Expertise</h3>
					<p>Our contractors are committed to serving the Stockton community. They understand local conditions, support local suppliers, and have deep knowledge of area requirements and preferences.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="team">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Our Network Standards</h2>
			<div class="team-grid">
				<div class="team-member">
					<div class="member-photo">
						<div class="photo-placeholder">🏆</div>
					</div>
					<h3>Licensed & Insured</h3>
					<p class="title">Professional Standards</p>
					<p>All contractors in our network are fully licensed and insured. They meet strict quality standards and maintain professional certifications to ensure your project is completed safely and correctly.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="team-member">
					<div class="member-photo">
						<div class="photo-placeholder">🔧</div>
					</div>
					<h3>Experienced Professionals</h3>
					<p class="title">Skilled Installation Teams</p>
					<p>Our contractors have years of experience in fence installation and repair. They bring expert knowledge, attention to detail, and professional problem-solving skills to every project.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="team-member">
					<div class="member-photo">
						<div class="photo-placeholder">📞</div>
					</div>
					<h3>Customer Service</h3>
					<p class="title">Professional Communication</p>
					<p>Our contractors prioritize clear communication throughout your project. From initial consultation to project completion, you'll receive professional service and regular updates on your fencing installation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="achievements">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Our Achievements & Milestones</h2>
			<div class="achievements-grid">
				<div class="achievement">
					<div class="achievement-number">25+</div>
