					<div class="cert-icon">⭐</div>
					<h3>BBB Accredited Business</h3>
					<p>A+ Rating with Better Business Bureau<br/>Accredited member since 2005</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="cert-item">
					<div class="cert-icon">🌿</div>
					<h3>Environmental Responsibility</h3>
					<p>Green building practices certified<br/>Sustainable material sourcing</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="community">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Community Involvement</h2>
			<div class="community-content">
				<p>We believe in giving back to the Stockton community that has supported our family business for over two decades. Our involvement includes:</p>
				
				<div class="community-grid">
					<div class="community-item">
						<div class="community-icon">🏀</div>
						<h3>Youth Sports Sponsorship</h3>
						<p>We proudly sponsor multiple Little League teams and youth basketball clubs throughout Stockton, providing uniforms, equipment, and field improvements.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="community-item">
						<div class="community-icon">🏠</div>
						<h3>Habitat for Humanity</h3>
						<p>Our crew regularly volunteers time and materials for Habitat for Humanity home builds, helping provide affordable housing for local families.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="community-item">
						<div class="community-icon">🎒</div>
						<h3>Educational Partnerships</h3>
						<p>We partner with local high schools and trade programs to provide internships and hands-on construction skills training to students.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="community-item">
						<div class="community-icon">🚨</div>
						<h3>First Responder Appreciation</h3>
						<p>We offer special discounts to police officers, firefighters, EMTs, and military personnel as our way of saying thank you for their service.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="testimonials">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>What Our Community Says</h2>
			<div class="testimonials-grid">
				<div class="testimonial">
					<p>"Mike and his team are absolute professionals. They installed a beautiful cedar fence around our entire backyard in just two days. The quality is outstanding and the price was very fair. Highly recommended!"</p>
					<div class="customer">
						<strong>Robert & Susan Chen</strong><br>
						<span>Tracy Residents</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial">
					<p>"After getting quotes from several companies, Stockton Fencing Co. stood out for their professionalism and attention to detail. They delivered exactly what they promised, on time and on budget."</p>
					<div class="customer">
						<strong>Jennifer Martinez</strong><br>
						<span>Manteca Business Owner</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial">
					<p>"We've used Stockton Fencing Co. for three different properties over the years. Their consistency in quality and service is remarkable. They treat every job like it's their most important one."</p>
					<div class="customer">
						<strong>David Thompson</strong><br>
						<span>Property Manager, Lodi</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Ready to Work with Stockton's Most Trusted Fencing Company?</h2>
			<p>Join thousands of satisfied customers who have chosen Stockton Fencing Co. for their residential and commercial fencing needs. Experience the difference that 25+ years of expertise and commitment to quality makes.</p>
			<a href="tel:888-682-0507" class="btn btn-quote">Call for Free Quote Now!</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

